            <lg xml:id="TK405">
<l>kallā voruvaṉ ṟakaimai talaippeytu</l>
<l>collāṭac cōrvu paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The self-conceit of an unlearned man will fade away, as soon as he speaks in an assembly (of thelearned).</l>
            </lg>
